Sentencas: Subsolidus equilibria in air in the La2O3 - Ga2O3 - NiO system were studied with the aim of obtaining information on possible interactions between a LaGaO3-based solid electrolyte and NiO during preparation of the anode in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the La2O3-Ga2O3-NiO system
